{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T06:22:29.742Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the official Claude API documentation and resources, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Defining Tools\""},{"type":"text","text":" in the Agent SDK refers to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"the process of specifying tool schemas as JSON definitions that describe what tools can do, so Claude can decide when to call them based on the user's request and the tool's capability"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Core Concept"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What Tool Definition Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tool use lets Claude call functions you define"},{"type":"text","text":" that integrate with external tools and APIs."}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"You define tools as JSON schemas\n    ↓\nClaude decides when to call based on user request + tool description\n    ↓\nClaude returns structured call (tool_use block)\n    ↓\nYour code executes the operation\n    ↓\nYou send back tool_result"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key insight"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Claude decides when to use tools based on the user's request and tool descriptions\"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tool Types"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Client Tools (You Execute)"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Type"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidt